snippet.title: HIGH ON KNIFE DLC RELEASE DATE
snippet.description:
OCTOBER 3RD: HIGH ON KNIFE DLC COMES TO XBOX, PLAYSTATION, AND PC.

Play the hilarious new DLC to High On Life, Xbox Game Pass' biggest launch of 2022!

Claymation by Taylor Wells (@taymations).
__

LEARN MORE ABOUT HIGH ON LIFE:

From Squanch Games comes High On Life. Humanity is being threatened by an alien cartel who wants to use them as drugs. It’s up to you to rescue and partner with charismatic, talking guns, take down Garmantuous and his gang, and save the world!

Play High On Life:

PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/p...
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/high...
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/15...
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/h...
